<h1 class="font-bold text-4xl mb-6">Design system</h1>
<div class="prose prose-lg prose-indigo">
  <p>A design system is a pre-configured set of standards and patterns to follow as you iterate on the application building process.</p>

  <p>Use this system as a guide but not necessarily a source of truth for exact use cases. It's meant to solve those repeatable problems aimed to help you increase speed and developer happiness.</p>
</div>

<ul class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-10">
  <li>
    <%= link_to systems_content_path, class: "border p-4 rounded-lg bg-white block hover:shadow-lg transition ease-in-out duration" do %>
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">Content</h3>
      <p class="mb-3 text-gray-600">Design patterns for everyday markup and content.</p>

      <span class="text-indigo-600">View more</span>
    <% end %>
  </li>
  <li>
    <%= link_to systems_forms_path, class: "border p-4 rounded-lg bg-white block hover:shadow-lg transition ease-in-out duration" do %>
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">Forms</h3>
      <p class="mb-3 text-gray-600">Inputs, controls, buttons, and more ready for quick use.</p>

      <span class="text-indigo-600">View more</span>
    <% end %>
  </li>
  <li>
    <%= link_to systems_elements_path, class: "border p-4 rounded-lg bg-white block hover:shadow-lg transition ease-in-out duration" do %>
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">Elements</h3>
      <p class="mb-3 text-gray-600">Atomic UI elements ready for your latest app.</p>

      <span class="text-indigo-600">View more</span>
    <% end %>
  </li>
  <li>
    <%= link_to systems_marketing_path, class: "border p-4 rounded-lg bg-white block hover:shadow-lg transition ease-in-out duration" do %>
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">Marketing</h3>
      <p class="mb-3 text-gray-600">Ready-to-use marketing components.</p>

      <span class="text-indigo-600">View more</span>
    <% end %>
  </li>
</ul>
